DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that a user can successfully change their password using valid credentials.
NAME: Test Change Password with Valid Inputs

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that a user can log in successfully with valid email and password, and is redirected to the account page.
NAME: Valid Login Test with Correct Credentials

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that attempting to change the password with an incorrect current password results in an error message.
NAME: Test Change Password with Incorrect Current Password

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that when the confirmation password does not match the new password, an appropriate error message is shown.
NAME: Test Change Password with Mismatched Confirmation Password

DESCRIPTION: This test verifies that logging in with an invalid email and password results in an error message.
NAME: Invalid Login Test with Incorrect Credentials
